'''Basa-Kontagora''' is a nearly extinct [[Kainji language]] of [[Nigeria]]. It is spoken in [[Mariga, Nigeria|Mariga]], [[Niger State]], near [[Kontagora]] and the [[Basa languages|Basa]] homeland.
